    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A naturally occurring oxide of titanium, having the chemical formula TiO2. It is a very stable compound with a high refractive index, used in food coloring, sunscreen, as a pigment, and in other applications.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
